  "text": "For isolated skeletal muscles, we previously observed ϳ30% decreased insulin-stimulated glucose uptake in AS160 Ϫ/Ϫ soleus (17) and Tbc1d1 Ϫ/Ϫ EDL muscles [CITATION_1] . But insulin-stimulated glucose uptake was normal in AS160 Ϫ/Ϫ",
